             was indicted for <rs id="t18230409-46-off239" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230409-46-off239" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230409-46-off239" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230409-46-cd240" type="crimeDate">7th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230409-46-off239 t18230409-46-cd240"></join>, at St. Leonard, Shoreditch, thirty-one yards of carpet, value 3 l. 10 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230409-46-victim491" type="victimName">
                           Benjamin 
                           Linsey
                        <interp inst="t18230409-46-victim491" type="surname" value="Linsey"></interp>
